title: The Loss of the S.S. Titanic
creator: Lawrence Beesley
description: LibriVox recording of The Loss of the S. S. Titanic by Lawrence Beesley, read by Allyson Hester. >This is a 1st hand account written by a survivor of the Titanic about that fateful night and the events leading up to it as well as the events that followed its sinking. - Summary written by Allyson Hester For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: Librivox;audiobook;nonfiction;disaster;iceberg,shipping;Titanic
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: Like I said; very good, very interesting.
